704546f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - St. James Place
704546f-a.text:
952-972 Fulton Street, south side, between St. James Place and
Grand Ave. The view shows the Criterion Theatre, at 968-972,formerly
known as Keeny's Theatre, not used for theatrical purposes for about
ten years.
May 31, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
